<!-- Android 12+ system-splash icon: the SEKAR box lockup (white NB box + pinwheel),
     tilted -6°, sized so its bounding circle fits inside the system's circular icon
     mask (~2/3 of the canvas). Pair with windowSplashScreenIconBackgroundColor = sage
     so the masked circle blends into the bootsplash canvas. The pre-Android-12
     cold-start path uses the same lockup via drawable-*/splash_logo.png. -->
